A production-ready Go API with Gin framework.

## What you need to modify

Your project has 9 files. You only need to care about 3:

| File | What it does | When to edit |
|------|-------------|-------------|
| `internal/server/handlers.go` | Route handlers and validation | **Every time** |
| `internal/server/server_test.go` | Tests for your handlers | **Every time** |
| `cmd/server/main.go` | Entry point, server wiring | Rarely |
| Others (Makefile, Dockerfile, go.mod) | Project infra | Almost never |

## Quick Start

```bash
go mod tidy
go run ./cmd/server
```

Visit **http://localhost:8080/health** to verify the server is running.

## Scripts

| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
