## API Endpoints

| Method | Path | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| GET | `/health` | Health check |
| GET | `/api/v1/users` | List all users |
| POST | `/api/v1/users` | Create a user (`email`, `name`) |

## Stack

- **Runtime**: Go 1.23
- **Web framework**: Gin (router, middleware, validation)
- **Database driver**: pgx (PostgreSQL — configure in production)
- **Logging**: zerolog (structured JSON logs)
- **CLI scaffolding**: cobra (for extended CLI needs)
- **Testing**: testing package + testify

## Environment Variables

| Variable | Default | Description |
|----------|---------|-------------|
| `ADDR` | `:8080` | Server listen address |
| `GIN_MODE` | `debug` | Set to `release` in production |
| `DATABASE_URL` | — | PostgreSQL connection string |
